Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名：相坂小夜　血型：不明　喜欢：不明　讨厌：不明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不错的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛屿是属于班长家的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过物权不属于雪广观光集团公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还完全就是私人用地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就得一直和她做朋友才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是下了诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了！涅吉老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让老师打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就稍微让自己努力去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您欣赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错哦  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名：明石裕奈　血型：A型　喜欢：父亲　讨厌：土气的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名：朝仓和美　血型：O型　喜欢：情感故事、照相机　讨厌：大恶人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  明日菜  你就原谅涅吉了吧怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正被弄成赤身裸体也不是第一次了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫「跟你没关系」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行啊  小木乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身泳装  实在是太大胆了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是没办法啊  小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸都红通了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是因为这个…呃…  太热的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对！是因为太热了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为太热了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用说那么多遍我也知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为太热…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名：绫濑夕映　血型：AB型　喜欢：读书　讨厌：学校功课
