Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样明日菜同学把涅吉老师救上来之后他们就能和好如初了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  鲨鱼什么的是不是有点过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这种时候就要用上古菲同学教的拳法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,adeat！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招——！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才的是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好像魔法一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没人看到也做得太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种恶作剧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明  明日菜同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名：叶加濑聪美　血型：B型　喜欢：机器人　讨厌：不科学的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}姓名：长谷川千雨　血型：B型　喜欢：小巧而有用的机器　讨厌：人拥挤的地方、无法预想的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝仓  到底要走到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  「哪里」是指…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有个目击地点什么的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是到处走走就会出来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你说到处走走  难道是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是不靠谱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦啦啦啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们该问的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名：Evangeline·A·K·McDowell　血型：不明　喜欢：茶茶丸泡的茶　讨厌：大蒜、上课
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没找到而已啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名：宫崎和香　血型：O型　喜欢：整理书籍　讨厌：男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名：村上夏美　血型：A型　喜欢：舞台　讨厌：自己、雀斑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  眼镜找不到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小古和小夏攻击的时候掉落了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说  掉在海里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  那个眼镜是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么您不早点说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁天亮的时候我们还能帮着找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  因为明日菜同学的事所以心里很乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很乱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓名：雪广绫香　血型：O型　喜欢：涅吉老师、花　讨厌：暴力而不讲道理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是涅吉就不许进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐  不行啊  这个可忘不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前开始就这么没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:17:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来就已经原谅他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出那种话的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我绝对不原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道他说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他可还是个小孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子也应该知道什么可以说什么不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候就会不假思索脱口而出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了  这和班长没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我啊  这跟明日菜同学你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就跟这儿生一宿气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天早上可还要早起  要睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早起？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师在海岸那边丢了眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不知道还能不能找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家已经说好早起帮助一起找的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他姐姐送给他的重要的眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为觉得被你讨厌受到了打击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到刚才才发觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  晚安了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  那种语气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是说都是我的错一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四叶五月　血型：A型　喜欢：料理、悠闲　讨厌：没什么特别…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zazie Rainyday　血型：B型　喜欢：小动物、人类　讨厌：没什么讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心脚边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…明日菜同学找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去游泳的时候偶尔发现的罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夜里…一个人游泳？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？一个人游泳不成吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有弄碎真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就走了  别再叫住我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了别…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  又把你叫住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常感谢你帮我找到了眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够看到这么漂亮的朝霞也是多亏了明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  现在就去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拖拖拉拉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那都是因为你说「和我没关系」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话让我很伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放着不管  你就太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是让人放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就别在说什么「没关系」了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我可是你的「搭档」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这很难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我才只有10岁的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这很让人难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨  笨蛋！我说的不是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.31,0:22:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜水艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老师～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各  各位同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  还这样偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛  反正他们也和好如初了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.93,0:23:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就轮到我来和涅吉老师吵架了
